### FIAP Hackaton — Architecture Diagram Analyzer API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

# Replace after a successful POST:
@analysisId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Health
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# POST /api/v1/analyses — Upload a diagram
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload JPEG diagram
# Point the < path to a real image on disk.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="diagram.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./diagram.jpg
------Boundary--

###

### Upload PNG diagram
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="diagram.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./diagram.png
------Boundary--

###

### Upload PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="architecture.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./architecture.pdf
------Boundary--

###

### Upload invalid type — expects 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="data.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello world
------Boundary--


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GET /api/v1/analyses/{id} — Analysis details
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get analysis by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses/{{analysisId}}
X-Correlation-Id: test-correlation-001

###

### Get analysis — not found (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GET /api/v1/analyses/{id}/status — Processing status
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses/{{analysisId}}/status

###

### Get status — not found (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/status


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GET /api/v1/analyses/{id}/report — AI report
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get AI-generated report (analysis must be Processed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses/{{analysisId}}/report

###

### Get report — not found (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/report

###

### Get report — not ready yet (expects 400 when status ≠ Processed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analyses/{{analysisId}}/report
